# Database:             postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:54322/postgres
# Studio (Dashboard):   http://localhost:54323
# Inbucket (Email):     http://localhost:54324
# Kong (API Gateway):   http://localhost:8000
# Auth:                 http://localhost:54321/auth/v1
# Storage:              http://localhost:54321/storage/v1

# ============================================
# QUICK START
# ============================================

# 1. Install Docker Desktop
# 2. Install Supabase CLI: npm i -g supabase
# 3. Start Supabase: supabase start
# 4. Copy this file to .env.local
# 5. Update keys from `supabase start` output
# 6. Run migrations: supabase db reset
# 7. Seed database: npm run seed
# 8. Start dev server: npm run dev
# 9. Access Studio: http://localhost:54323
